    public class AbstractDotShapeProposalProvider
extends org.eclipse.xtext.common.ui.contentassist.TerminalsProposalProvider
    Represents a generated, default implementation of superclass TerminalsProposalProvider. Methods are dynamically dispatched on the first parameter, i.e., you can override them with a more concrete subtype.
